Dexia Holder Holding Communal Wins New Guarantees, L’Echo Says

-- B y   J i m   B r u n s d e n
-- 
2011-09-21T06:17:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/dexia-holder-holding-communal-wins-new-guarantees-l-echo-says.html
Dexia SA (DEXB)  shareholder Holding
Communal SA will be granted new guarantees of 200 million euros
($274 million) to 300 million euros by  Belgium ’s regional
governments,  L’Echo  reported without saying where it obtained
the information.  The regions have attached conditions to providing the new
guarantees, including that Holding Communal “abandons its
policy of diversification and refocuses on its stake in Dexia,”
the newspaper said.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Jim Brunsden in Brussels at 
 jbrunsden@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Anthony Aarons at   aaarons@bloomberg.net . 